@startuml 00_modello_concettuale
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80
title CLS-00 - Modello concettuale ACL
skinparam shadowing false
hide empty members

class ACLEntry <<Entity>> {
  +id : ACLEntryId
  +level : int?
  +group : GroupId?
  +profile_join : JoinOp = OR
  +subject_join : JoinOp = AND
}

class SubjectRef <<ValueObject>> {
  +kind : USER | PUBLIC | SERVICE
  +id : str?
}

class ResourceRef <<ValueObject>> {
  +type : str
  +id : str | global | *
}

class OperationSpec <<ValueObject>> {
  +name : OperationName
  +read_only : bool
  +inheritable : bool = true
  +protected : bool = false
}

class Profile <<ValueObject>> {
  +level : int
  +groups : frozenset[GroupId]
  +version : int?
  +anonymous()
}

class GroupId <<ValueObject>>

class Permission <<Enum>> {
  ALLOW
  DENY
}

class Decision <<Enum>> {
  ALLOWED
  DENIED
}

class JoinOp <<Enum>> {
  AND
  OR
}

ACLEntry --> SubjectRef : subject
ACLEntry --> ResourceRef : resource
ACLEntry --> OperationSpec : operation name
ACLEntry --> Permission : permission
ACLEntry --> JoinOp : joins
Profile "1" o-- "*" GroupId : groups
OperationSpec --> Decision : contribuisce a

note bottom of ACLEntry
  Unita atomica persistita:
  chi, su cosa, quale operazione,
  verdetto e criteri di profilo.
end note

legend
  Navigazione: [[01_acl_entry.puml ACLEntry]] |
  [[02_soggetti_risorse_operazioni.puml Subject/Resource/Operation]] |
  [[03_profili_permessi_decisioni.puml Profili/decisioni]] |
  [[../componenti/00_mappa_componenti.puml Componenti]]
endlegend
@enduml
